				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\beta $\end{document}β solar wind conditions, plasma outflows from reconnection sites may be visible in soft X-ray.

